Description: itertools and builtins for asyncio and mixed iterables (Avalan PPA transitive)
 aioitertools is a small library that mirrors the Python standard
 library's `itertools` module and several builtins (`all`, `any`,
 `map`, `next`, `zip`, ...) for async iterables. This package is built
 for the Avalan PPA because aiobotocore (Avalan's `vendors` extra,
 reached via aioboto3) requires it and Noble's archive does not carry
 it. Pinned at 0.13.0.
